what people are hearing
from Democrats now
is anti-Donald Trump?

07:27.133 --> 07:30.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
How do you both do this,
the positive things
you're talking about, and
remain this relentless

07:31.766 --> 07:35.400 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
anti-Trump machine that many
people think the Democrats are?

07:35.400 --> 07:40.100 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
THOMAS PEREZ: Well,
we can't match Trump
tweet for tweet, because
distracting Donald frequently

07:40.100 --> 07:42.100 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
out there.

07:42.100 --> 07:46.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I'm sure, at the G20,
everyone was talking about
John Podesta's tweets.

07:46.000 --> 07:51.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so when you -- and then
you have this misnamed voter
integrity commission, which

07:52.033 --> 07:54.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
is a voter suppression
commission.

07:54.666 --> 07:58.200 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we can't allow all of
the relentless conflict
and chaos that emanates
from this administration

08:02.933 --> 08:04.933 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
to take our eye off the ball.

08:04.933 --> 08:08.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
That's what today was
about with Leader Pelosi
and Senator Schumer.

08:08.166 --> 08:12.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It was about telling the
American people we are the party
that's fighting for a better

08:12.333 --> 08:14.433 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
future for folks, for everyone.

08:14.433 --> 08:18.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We're the party that's going
to make sure that you get that
good job that pays a decent

08:18.866 --> 08:21.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
wage that allows
you to have dignity.

08:21.933 --> 08:23.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And we have to do that.

08:23.966 --> 08:27.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And that's exactly what I do
everywhere I go, Judy, because
it is so important to tell

08:27.666 --> 08:31.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
people what we stand for
and who we stand with.

08:31.333 --> 08:35.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Tom Perez, the
chairman of the Democratic
Party, thank you very much.

08:35.266 --> 08:35.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
THOMAS PEREZ: Pleasure
to be with you.
